Wallhack_maze

Just a maze of invisible walls.
To make it more "exciting" you can shoot through 1 wall as soon as you got 2 walls between u and the enemy ur safe.
you can see the beginning of the walls on the floor.
you start with an m4/90 bullets
when u find the secret you come to a room with ALL weaponspawners (gotten from a prefab on this site)

>>> The walls aren't as big as in the pictures. <<<

Have Fun!
